          <div class="foot-saying">
            <p>应试公关成就你的人生</p>
            <p>pr examination achievements of your life</p>
          </div>
          <div class="foot-contact">
            <p class="foot-dress">地址：青岛市市南区香港中路36号招银大厦1707</p>
            <p class="foot-tel">电话：0532-89999108 / 89999508 / 89999608</p>
